# Mainnet Update: 2D-to-3D  

@404-gen・17 

Our *most* requested feature **2D-to-3D** has launched and is now live across all Validators on Mainnet :peperave: 

Whilst **Text-to-3D** generations have produced strong results, maintaining consistent tone and style across assets required more nuanced prompting. With **2D-to-3D** Creators can now transform 2D images into fully textured 3D models giving them ultimate creative control over their 3D Projects ✨ 
## For Miners  ⛏️ 

> - 20% of all Synthetic Traffic Tasks are now **2D-to-3D**.
> - Synthetic 2D Prompts are being generated by our friends at **SN12**. For more details: https://discord.com/channels/799672011265015819/1179081290289528864/1423031676648427551

**PR:** https://github.com/404-Repo/three-gen-subnet/pull/116

If you have any questions please let us know. You can find us here or you can open a ticket in our discord server: https://discord.gg/404gen

Team 404.
